data.description: UPDATE: ***With full price offer, seller will pay $20k toward solar panel loan, which is assumable. VA Loan is also Assumable.*** Pool with a view, 3 car detached garage, extra storage space, an RV canopy and solar panels...where can you find a property with not just 1, 2, or 3... but 6 major attractors? Not only does this unique home provide significant space, modern touches, features to make insurance companies satisfied, peace & quiet, but it also has all of the toys & NO HOA! The in-ground pool is less than 5 years old with a view from the balcony that affords your own serene oasis (and comes with an Aquabot!), there's a 2 car garage that has another garage on the South side with superior functionality, a shed for garden tools or extra storage space, 960 Sq. Ft. RV storage with 30 amp hook-up. Crawlspace has been encapsulated & equipped with a dehumidifier. Effective year is 2005 BUT major upgrades were undertaken from 2018-now. Outdoor shower with hot water. The study has wood burning fireplace. Not only does the fireplace add warmth, but so does the natural light to make the room perfect for a personal library, convert into another bedroom or otherwise. The family room comes with a wood burning stove - perfect for various uses. Above the family room is vast storage space. The master has a mini-split, added by the previous seller prior to the HVAC being replaced in 2022. Bathrooms have granite countertops. Check out the upgrades as follows but don't forget to see what upgrades have been completed since 2018 in the documents section: roof on house replaced 2022, detached buildings roofed 2018, Pool installed 2019,  960 Sq ft detached RV covered parking installed 2021, 14.00KW/200AMPS, Tier 2 Solar Panels installed in 2023. All information that is important to the buyer is their responsibility to verify.
